title: Ep. 431 - Popatlal Proposes Koyal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Taarak and Jethalal warn Popatlal to stay away from Koyal and forget her. In a indirect way, they decide to ask Koyal her opinion. Popatlal gets excited when her expectations match with his personality.

title: Ep. 432 - Popatlal Throws A Party - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: After Taarak, Anjali and Koyal go to collect Koyal's visa, Popatlal announces to the society members about the function. The society members keep guessing the reason for the party. Taarak and Anjali get furious on Koyal for doing timepass.

title: Ep. 433 - Chaos All Around - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal comes to the hall and everyone starts asking him questions. He asks everyone to gather around so that he can say it to everyone, but people are unable to fir in that space and chaos is created all around.

title: Ep. 434 - Popatlal Takes The Poison - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Everyone tries to stop Popatlal, but he does not listen and intakes the poison. Suddenly, the poison starts reacting and Popatlal falls on the ground. What will happen next? How will the people of Gokuldham society help them?

title: Ep. 435 - Goons In The Gokuldham Society - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Some strange people come inside society and demands money for the festivals. Daya, Komal, and Babita are buying vegetables and encounters them on the way. They start asking each and everyone a large sum of money as donations.

title: Ep. 436 - A Surptise Treat For Abdul - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Abdul s keeping fast and eats his food alone in the evening. But this time he is surprised as everyone gets him delicious snacks and offers to open his fast with them. Abdul is deeply touched by the efforts made by everyone.

title: Ep. 437 - Competition In Gokuldham - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The society members gather to celebrate Krishna Jayanthi and are excited about the competition. The ladies and gents of the society give equal competition to each other.

title: Ep. 438 - Daya Is In Danger - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: There is a lot of excitement among the society members as to who will win the competition. When the ladies start performing for the competition, Daya lands up in a dangerous situation. Will the competition stop for the sake of Daya?

title: Ep. 439 - Jethalal Is Heartbroken - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya falls down and gets injured during the task and she is rushed to the hospital. Knowing about the accident, Sunderlal starts for Gokuldham.  Daya's family and the society members pray for her speedy recovery.

title: Ep. 440 - Daya Responds - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The doctors try their best, but Daya is still unconscious. Tapu Sena prepares food for the society members who are in the hospital. Jethalal tries his best to bring Daya back into her consciousness. Will Daya recover?

title: Ep. 451 - Singing Competition In Gokuldham - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Gokuldham society receives a certificate from Times Of India Group for its participation in Times Green Ganesha. Anand Ji comes as a guest in Gokuldham to judge the singing competition. The society members display their talent in singing.

title: Ep. 452 - Anand Ji As Judge - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Anand Ji announces Komal and Bhide as the winners of the singing competition. Taarak cherishes the memories of Anand Ji and shares the memories with everyone. Anand Ji spent a gala time with the society members.

title: Ep. 453 - Rishi Kapoor And Neetu Kapoor Visit Gokuldham - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The ladies of Gokuldham practice Garba and are excited about it. While practicing Garba in the clubhouse, they are shocked when they see Rishi Kapoor and Neetu Kapoor. Rishi Kapoor and Neetu Kapoor come in search of Daya.

title: Ep. 454 - Daya Teaches Garba To Rishi And Neetu - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Rishi and Neetu fool the ladies by hiding their real identity and they ask Daya to teach garba. Later, the ladies are shocked when they realize that they have met the real superstars. Rishi and Neetu explain the ladies about their upcoming movie.

title: Ep. 455 - Jethalal Is Irritated - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal almost loses a contract and is very upset about it. Jethalal shows his irritation upon everyone and he even breaks Popatlal's umbrella. Jethalal and Popatlal have a very big fight in the society compound.
